{"word":"G4207 - πόῤῥωθεν - pórrhōthen - por'-rho-then - Afar off","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πόῤῥωθεν</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pórrhōthen</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">por'-rho-then</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Afar off</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தூரத்தில் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"from afar, afar off"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4206 - πόῤῥω - pórrhō - por'-rho/4206\">G4206</a> with adverbial enclitic of source; <i>from far</i>, or (by implication) <i>at a distance</i>, that is, <i>distantly:</i> - afar off.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}